<p><a name="Physics" id="Physics"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Radioactive_waste&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Physics">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Physics</span></h3>
